data.description: The 2018 fully furnished Guest Apartment/second home is aprox 800 sq ft and includes a bedroom, living room, kitchen, and bath, the mancave is also aprox. 800 sq ft... the square footage is included in the homes total square footage as well as the bedroom and bath in the total MLS bedrooms and baths.   9 bay garage with a double garage door entrance is NOT included in any square footage on MLS. Space and location is key just this home is just minutes from restaurants, shopping, the interstate, schools, and Maxwell Air Force Base!  Tucked away on your gorgeous 1 acre lot with a pool, hot tub, fenced yard, 11 garage spaces, storm shelter, and your own separate apartment house.  You're greeted on the large elegant front porch with plenty of room to sit and enjoy the view. As you enter the front door on your left is living/study/music room with gorgeous built ins, and on your right a large oversized dining room dressed with crown moldings, plantation shutters throughout, and wood flooring. The family room is grand with its 2 story ceiling and balcony and it all has views to the sparkling saltwater pool in back. Then enter the spacious custom kitchen which has 2 ovens,  and a large work island. The double pantry is nice  as well as the laundry room with another set of cabinets and a utility sink. A second stairwell to the top floor is conveniently located in the laundry area. The private master suite downstairs has a large garden tub and shower, and 3 closets. Upstairs there are 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, 2 sitting areas and a very large bonus room. The salt water pool is ready for entertaining and the covered porch that stretches across the back of the home is perfect for relaxing.   The first  2 car garage gives you storage space or a gym/work area.  The 2018 addition is a show stopper with granite, full kitchen, bedroom, bathroom, living room, 9 car garage, storm shelter and the biggest mancave bonus area upstairs you have seen bar and pool table included!
